\frac{17}{8} & 34 & \sqrt[5]{19} & \ln9\\
\frac{\pi}{4} & 0.34 & e^{7} & \sin(1)\\
2^{2^{2}} & \tan^{-1}(1) & 12 & 10^{1000}
\end{array}\right]
\end{gathered}
\]

\end_inset

Answers on page 
